item.title: Need help Im stuck somewhere
item.dc:creator: @gunztheduel gunztheduel
item.description:
@gunztheduel wrote:

Question 1:

I was on my server exploring Castlewars using ::noclip command and I try to go down via the ladder and stairs. I click on them but i don’t go down. Why?

Answer:

The ladder or stairs have not been scripted. If the whole of Runescape was to be scripted, it would take years, or so, said from a Moparscape moderator.

Question 2:

I seem to be stuck on the top floor of Castlewars Arena. Why? How can I get out?

Answer:

There are various glitches in the game. They are unscripted, as mentioned in the answer for Question 1. To get out of that glitch, simply teleport to another place.
